cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the area of place recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The use of robotics and navigation suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also involves the development of a novel methodology, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
